description: Novus Acquisition & Development Corp., through its subsidiary, WCIG Insurance Service, Inc., operates as an insurance company in California It offers health policies in CBD concentrate cannabis space; benefit plans, such as dental vision, hearing, and telemedicine; and THC health plans. The company was formerly known as BrandQuest Development Group, Inc. and changed its name to Novus Acquisition & Development Corp. in April 2009. Novus Acquisition & Development Corp. was incorporated in 1996 and is based in Miami, Florida.
